#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Access Control:</strong> Limit sensitive files to relevant team "
"members."
msgstr ""
"<strong>アクセス制御:</strong> 機密ファイルは関連するチームメンバーに限定して"
"ください。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong> – Advanced financial management and reporting."
msgstr "<strong>会計</strong> – 高度な財務管理とレポーティング。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Alerts &amp; Notifications:</strong> Ensure deadlines are met."
msgstr "<strong>アラート&amp; 通知:</strong> で期日を確実に管理します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Assignments:</strong> Allocate engineers, site managers, and "
"subcontractors."
msgstr ""

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Billing:</strong> Invoice based on work completion or project\n"
"                    milestones."
msgstr ""
"<strong>請求:</strong> 作業完了またはプロジェクトのマイルストーンに\n"
"                    基づいて請求します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Calendar Views:</strong> Visualize overlapping tasks and adjust\n"
"                    workloads."
msgstr ""
"<strong>カレンダービュー:</strong> 重複するタスクを可視化し、\n"
"作業負荷を調整します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Chatter &amp; Communication:</strong> Collaborate internally using "
"notes\n"
"                    and messages linked to opportunities."
msgstr ""
"<strong>チャターとコミュニケーション:</strong> 案件に関連付けられたメモやメッ"
"セージを使用して、\n"
"                    社内で円滑に情報共有・連携できます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Client Portal:</strong> Allow customers to track the status of "
"their\n"
"                    requests."
msgstr ""
"<strong>顧客ポータル:</strong> 顧客が自分自身のリクエストの状況を確認\n"
"                    できるようにします。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Construction Builder</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>建設ビルダ</strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Construction Developer</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>建設開発業者</strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "<strong>Cost Analysis:</strong> Link labor to project expenses."
msgid "<strong>Cost Analysis:</strong> Link labour to project expenses."
msgstr "<strong>コスト分析:</strong> 人件費をプロジェクト経費に紐付けます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Daily Logs:</strong> Employees enter hours per task."
msgstr "<strong>日次記録：</strong> 従業員はタスクごとの時間を入力します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Document Requests:</strong> Send requests with follow up activities."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ドキュメント:</strong> 申請とフォローアップ活動を送信してください。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Employees</strong> – Manage workforce, skills, and certifications."
msgstr "<strong>従業員</strong> – 従業員、スキル、資格を管理します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Fleet</strong> – Track machinery, vehicles, and maintenance "
"schedules."
msgstr ""
"<strong>フリート</strong> – 機械、車両、および整備スケジュールを追跡します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Helpdesk App</strong> provides responsive customer service, tracks "
"inquiries,\n"
"            and resolves issues efficiently."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ヘルプデスクアプリ</strong> 」は、迅速な顧客サービスを提供し、問い合"
"わせを追跡し、\n"
"            問題を効率的に解決します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>How to use it:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>利用方法</strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>In such situation, feel free to experiment with this database and "
"then\n"
"                        to create a new one for your own usage.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>このような状況では、このデータベースで自由に試してみてから、\n"
"                        ご自身の用途に合わせて新しいものを作成してください。"
"</strong>"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Inventory App</strong> manages materials, tracks deliveries, and "
"monitors site\n"
"            stock to prevent delays or shortages."
msgstr ""
"<strong>在庫アプリ</strong> 資材を管理し、納品状況を追跡し、現場の在庫を監視"
"することで遅延や\n"
"            不足を防止します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Invoice from Quotation:</strong> Convert approved quotes into "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"<strong>見積書から請求書作成:</strong> 承認済み見積書を請求書に変換します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Invoicing App</strong> ensures timely billing, automates recurring "
"invoices, and\n"
"            integrates with project milestones."
msgstr ""
"<strong>請求アプリ</strong> 請求のタイミングを確実に管理し、定期請求を自動"
"化。\n"
"            プロジェクトのマイルストーンとも連携します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Keep documentation organized:</strong>\n"
"                            Centralize contracts, drawings, and permits for "
"easy access."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ドキュメントを整理して保管:</strong>\n"
"                            契約書、図面、許可証を一元管理し、簡単にアクセス"
"できるようにします。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Leads &amp; Opportunities:</strong> Record incoming inquiries from\n"
"                    emails, forms, or calls."
msgstr ""
"<strong> リード・案件：</strong>\n"
"                    メール、フォーム、電話からの問い合わせを記録します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Milestones:</strong> Define major project achievements."
msgstr ""
"<strong>マイルストン:</strong> プロジェクトの主要な達成目標を定義します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Mobile Execution:</strong> Record time, materials used, and capture "
"photos\n"
"                or client signatures on site."
msgstr ""
"<strong>モバイル実行:</strong> 現場で作業時間や使用資材を記録し、\n"
"                写真や顧客の署名を取得できます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Monitor stock proactively:</strong> Avoid\n"
"                            project delays by tracking inventory in real-"
"time."
msgstr ""
"<strong>在庫を積極的にモニタリング:</strong> リアルタイムで\n"
"                            在庫を把握し、プロジェクトの遅延を防ぎましょう。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Online Approval:</strong> Enable online customer approval."
msgstr "<strong>オンライン承認:</strong> 顧客のオンライン承認を可能にします。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>PDF Output:</strong> Send branded quotations for client approval."
msgstr ""
"<strong>PDF出力:</strong> 顧客の承認を得るために、企業ブランドに沿った見積書"
"を送付します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Payment Tracking:</strong> Monitor outstanding client payments."
msgstr "<strong>支払追跡:</strong> 未払いの顧客支払いを監視します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Pipeline Management:</strong> Visualize lead stages and prioritize\n"
"                    follow-ups."
msgstr ""
"<strong>パイプライン管理:</strong> リードステージを可視化し、フォローアップを"
"優先順位付けします。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Pricing &amp; Discounts:</strong> Adjust based on project size or "
"client\n"
"                    agreements."
msgstr ""
"<strong>価格設定・割引:</strong> プロジェクト規模またはクライアント契約に基づ"
"き\n"
"                    調整します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Prioritization:</strong> Assign critical tickets to senior staff."
msgstr ""
"<strong>優先順位付け:</strong> 重要なチケットを上級スタッフに割り当てます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Product Prices:</strong> Capture prices by suppliers to make the\n"
"                    best moves."
msgstr ""
"<strong>プロダクト価格:</strong> 仕入先の価格を把握して、\n"
"                   最適な判断を下しましょう。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Progress Reporting:</strong> Compare actual time vs planned."
msgstr "<strong>進捗報告:</strong> 実績時間と計画時間を比較します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Project Files:</strong> Attach blueprints, permits, and contracts."
msgstr ""
"<strong>プロジェクトファイル:</strong> 設計図、許可証、契約書を添付してくださ"
"い。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Project Updates</strong>: Capture project snapshots along the way "
"from the dashboard."
msgstr ""

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Purchase App </strong>helps you managing requests for proposal, your "
"suppliers\n"
"            and contractors."
msgstr ""
"<strong>購買アプリ</strong>提案依頼、仕入先や業者の管理を\n"
"            サポートします。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Purchase Orders:</strong> Create purchase order for needed products\n"
"                    and services."
msgstr ""
"<strong>購買オーダ:</strong> 必要なプロダクトおよびサービスの購買オーダ\n"
"                    を作成します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Quotation Templates:</strong> Predefine templates for recurrent\n"
"                    offers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>見積テンプレート:</strong> 繰り返し使う提案書をあらかじめ\n"
"                    定義できます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Reordering:</strong> Automate purchase orders for low-stock items."
msgstr ""
"<strong>再オーダ:</strong> 在庫が少ないプロダクトの購買オーダを自動化します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Reporting &amp; Invoicing:</strong> Generate detailed intervention "
"reports\n"
"                and invoice billable work when applicable."
msgstr ""
"<strong>レポーティング・請求</strong> 詳細な作業レポートを生成し、\n"
"                該当する場合は請求対象の作業に対して請求書を発行します。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Resource Allocation:</strong> Assign workers, subcontractors, and\n"
