#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>CRM module</strong> helps construction companies capture leads "
"from multiple\n"
"            sources, track communications, and schedule follow-ups.  <br/"
">You can prioritize\n"
"            high-value opportunities and turn inquiries into profitable "
"projects."
msgstr ""
"<strong>CRMモジュール</strong>建設会社が複数のチャネルからリードを獲得し、や"
"り取りの履歴を追跡し、フォローアップを\n"
"            スケジューリングするのに役立ちます。  <br/>価値の高い案件に優先順"
"位をつけ、\n"
"            問い合わせを収益性の高いプロジェクトへと転換できます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Field Service App</strong> helps you manage on-site "
"interventions such as\n"
"            follow-up works, warranty services, or urgent client requests. "
"Technicians can access\n"
"            tasks, log hours, and report outcomes directly from their mobile "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"<strong>フィールドサービスアプリ</strong> は、フォローアップ作業、保証サービ"
"ス、緊急の顧客対応などの\n"
"            現地作業を管理するのに役立ちます。技術者はモバイルデバイスから直"
"接タスクにアクセスし、\n"
"            作業時間を記録し、結果を報告できます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Planning app</strong> schedules tasks, allocates employees, and "
"coordinates\n"
"            equipment use across multiple construction sites."
msgstr ""
"<strong>計画アプリ</strong> を活用すれば、複数の建設現場においてタスクのスケ"
"ジュール設定、\n"
"            従業員の割り当て、設備使用の調整を行うことができます。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Projects App</strong> allows you to manage tasks, assign "
"resources, and\n"
"            create milestones for each construction project."
msgstr ""
"<strong>プロジェクトアプリ</strong>を使えば、各建設プロジェクトのタスク管"
"理、\n"
"            リソースの割り当て、マイルストーンの作成が可能です。"

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Sales App</strong> enables rapid creation of professional "
"quotations.\n"
"            You can use product kits for materials, apply discounts, and "
"send polished proposals\n"
"            directly to clients."
msgstr ""
